{"title":"公社搭起上天梯","authors":["赁常彬"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":11,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社搭起上天梯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赁常彬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大川小川归大海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社百花开："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高产卫星飞满天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粮食堆成万座山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄稼汉把工人当，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高炉炼铁又炼钢；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇女解开绊脚索，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走出厨房去干活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇女干活样样强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绣花绣朵缝衣裳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫩芽芽，朵朵花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幼儿园里笑哈哈；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸡冠花，老菜红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福院中乐无穷；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要甜甜不过糖精，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福生活甜进心！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社搭起上天梯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天堂就是共产主义！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}